# Summary
This documentation page describes the integration between Amplitude and Klaviyo, allowing users to export cohorts from Amplitude to Klaviyo for targeted email marketing campaigns, including setup steps in both platforms and how to send cohorts with proper user mapping where Klaviyo requires valid email format as user ID.

